com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.boundarymatch
Class MatchedSegment

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.boundarymatch.MatchedSegment
public class MatchedSegment
extends java.lang.Object

Contains the information about the linesegments (or subsegments) in other Features which match a given LineSegment. If one of the matching segments is identical, the hasExactMatch flag is set.

computeReferenceInsertedVertices

public java.util.List computeReferenceInsertedVertices()
Creates a list of inserted vertices for a Reference segment. Vertices are inserted into the segment as long as they are not equal to one of the endpoints of the segment. Note that no explicit check is made to ensure that short linesegments are not created as a result of the insertion. However, this should never happen, since an inserted vertex which might create a short line segment should have been snapped to an endpoint already.
